During this one-week program, an exceptional group of rising sophomores and juniors will convene at Capital One’s corporate headquarters outside Washington, D.C., to explore and develop the software and technology skills valued by today’s top employers.\nThe week includes a great series of trainings on emerging technologies and trends, a rigorous hackathon and presentation to Capital One leadership and a slew of fun activities throughout the week. You will have the opportunity to meet recent college grads now employed at Capital One and network with other students from top colleges and universities. This week we encourage to learn something new and challenge yourself in this exciting corporate setting!
